The paper is about the theory and applications of automata and formal languages, which are fundamental topics in computer science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
